# Test verification receipts live here.
#
# Each scope writes one JSON file (e.g., mobile.json). Pre-push hook reads
# these and validates that every affected file in the branch is covered by a
# passing receipt generated within the last 24 hours. Receipts are tracked in
# git so reviewers can see which scoped test command the author verified.
#
# Mobile receipts use related Jest tests for affected mobile TS/TSX files,
# not the full mobile suite and not content-hash matching.
#
# Generate with: bash scripts/record-test-receipt.sh <scope>
# Validate with: bash scripts/verify-test-receipts.sh